data.description: Prepare to be blown away by this STUNNING Lancaster model by Quality Built Homes, just 3 years young. Why build a new and basic standard home if you can have this high-quality one ready to move in?   This immaculate home will not disappoint! The homeowners made lots of tasteful improvements, from the inviting patios to the gleaming wood flooring to the customized wall trim design and the seating bench with extra storage and hooks in the mudroom.  This Almost 5,000 total sqft colonial, with a natural light-filled open floor plan, has something for everyone! It features FIVE large bedrooms, three full bathrooms, and a one-half bathroom.   The deluxe gourmet kitchen showcases granite countertops, Ralston maple cabinets, soft-closing drawers, and undercabinet Lighting. Stainless steel appliances with a gas cooktop, double oven, and a large island. The kitchen opens to the cozy 20x17 family room with a marble gas fireplace and a gorgeous coffered ceiling. The separate office space on the main floor is perfect for working from home or homeschooling. It features French doors with a transom window and a customized designed wall trim. Upstairs, you will find the luxurious main suite with an angled tray, crown molding, and two large walk-in closets. The deluxe master bathroom has two shower heads and a pedestal tub.  For added convenience, there is a laundry room on the upper floor. The finished basement with a 9ft ceiling includes a large rec room, the 5th bedroom, and a full bathroom.  Enjoy the large new patio outdoors with a fire pit stone area with seating, perfect for relaxing or entertaining. A new patio was also added to the side of the house, coming in through the mud room for convenience. This gorgeous colonial also features a home water filtration system and water softener tankless water heater.  Located at the desirable Laurel Preserve with a very low HOA fee, only $27 per month! Great location, has an easy commute to NAS Pax River Base and shopping, is around 2 miles to the Three Notch Trail, and convenient to Washington DC.
